ca.sharcnet.nerve.docnav.dom

Class Node

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.sharcnet.nerve.docnav.dom.Node
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<Node>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CommentNode, DoctypeNode, Document, ElementNode, InstructionNode, TextNode

    public abstract class Node
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Node>
    A node is a DOM object which may have a parent node, child nodes and/or attributes. The Node class is the parent class to all document nodes, and has no default specified type.
